step_data.thought:
Looking at the current state of the page, I can see that I've already successfully accomplished the goal of viewing the list of VIP Customers. The filter has been applied, as indicated by the 'Active filters: Group: VIP Customers' text visible on the page, and the table now shows only the 14 customers who belong to the 'VIP Customers' group.
